Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匯聚的祈願  在石板開啟接點後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.22,0:01:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是過了多久呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的舞台先是成形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.52,0:01:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在光輝中茁壯成為應有之姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.65,0:01:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破壞與秩序交織為凡塵事理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.62,0:02:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變的浪潮則在隨後到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等守護的力量雕零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.51,0:02:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都將墜入渾沌深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象征人世滄桑的循環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將再次畫下句號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.90,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在最後  我希望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白  快點醒醒  這只是一場夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑  你還沒睡醒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我要說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點清醒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還要溺在夢境多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓  準備去上學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣可不行啊  貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.53,0:03:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要整理書包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  這是夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這也是那石板帶來的超自然現象吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你這麽幹脆就接受了  真叫人意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.97,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的缺席給我一種奇怪缺失感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽了你的說明我才明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來這是因為那場夢不夠完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.07,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧我準備了好多說服你的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下還真沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒義務滿足你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  這還真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.54,0:04:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告訴我這只是一場夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.72,0:04:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就突然從這過去的幻象中醒悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因為你的一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麽大規模的噱頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然三兩下就被我們破除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我們囚禁在夢裏的人  到底有什麽企圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囚禁…嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.45,0:04:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許事情不是我們所想的這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.24,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.37,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道反你應該也知道  我們身處是誰的夢境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會夢見這種無聊透頂的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可能是你這喚醒我的人做的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再扣除那些已經死去的他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們終於回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫  你去哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應付那條黑犬是你的職責啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.53,0:05:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在無法判斷該不該喚醒這一場夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我們都太心軟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點醒醒  小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你今天到底是怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早一直吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.43,0:05:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑  好吵哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.35,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要特務隊部署完畢  隨時都能進行鎮壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  聽起來萬無一失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好  淡島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽我們就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.18,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.07,0:06:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三王權者  赤王周防尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我誠摯歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也迎戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位  可以占用一點時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員拔刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫跟平坂都去哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在東張西望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一幕好像在哪看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是什麽時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當然會這麽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.05,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  他們又混水摸魚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:08:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都已經發現這只是重覆理想場景的夢境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是獨具慧眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.69,0:08:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也察覺到自己只是五條須久那夢境的產物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這該怎麽說呢  須久那的願望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一陷入這樣的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.37,0:08:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥氣的磐叔也就自然原汁原味地再次登台亮相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過居然還要把我這個大叔一起拉來陪大家胡鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這夢還真是天真單純啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子只是希望能看看  磐舟天雞親自上戰場的帥氣身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得我都不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.19,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須久那願意在夢裏尋求和我們並肩作戰的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我由衷喜悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.07,0:09:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也因為這樣  有句話我不得不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是以破除舊習  以革新為目的的綠之盟Jungle
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位  我要給你們最後的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.63,0:09:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命  夢中的吾王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.14,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬是擺脫這個夢境嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個讓人放心不下的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連死了也不能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.49,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還要在夢中沉溺多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.87,0:09:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣逃避現實不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.95,0:09:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了盡可能維持現狀  不想采取多余的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這麽做  接下來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我以研究者的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.85,0:10:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀察眼前這名為夢的現實所做出的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.06,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過戲就演到這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟也有其他人也像你一樣醒悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就進入下個階段吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂浮在這舒適的夢裡  想想的突破方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽接下來  邊想邊漂浮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾輩討厭想事情  就陪你一起漂浮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你等在外面  世理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家的人睡得東倒西歪  實在不能見人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  是我突然來找你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  我現在也沒心情喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  這杯紅豆年糕湯果然沒有白準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  夜班剛結束的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這是有什麽事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.10,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙  你覺得現在的生活充實嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就跟人在街道旁約會  應該算吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  或許這也算是一部份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世理  你今天怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得現在的日子很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不知道該不該說充實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我喜歡這樣的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是件好事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但未免好過頭了  一切都太過美滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事一帆風順
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬無一失  水到渠成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一切都稱心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  正因為是稱心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.49,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我不禁懷疑「現在」到底是不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙  你沒有這種感覺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並沒有你所說的那種…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得充實的現在  就像是南柯一夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.84,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  第二方法論補充說明裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同質效果與共振賦予體論證是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.22,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是跟石板一起出土那些碎片的摘要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜刀神  請給我茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.57,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綁不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好  淡島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.02,0:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.02,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事…應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  今天又混水摸魚去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了  你無聊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓磐叔我來陪你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想學學怎麽打花牌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要玩那種過時的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.42,0:14:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你最近怎麽開始願意教我東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.97,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為啊  把智慧傳承下去是大人的使命嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.11,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.40,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,編寫程序時怎樣的核心架構最有效率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.36,0:15:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打花牌跟寫程序有什麽好傳承的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.49,0:15:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好吧  就當作是消磨時間也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽啊  你這不是躍躍欲試的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  快點教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿比古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是指哪個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.31,0:15:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一同歡笑與奮戰  感覺真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你的關系也維持原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不懂你在說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過怎麽說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.15,0:15:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有股焦慮  也覺得有種哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不懂為什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是詩人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  應該是更殘酷的現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.13,0:16:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個夢裏有些五條須久那不知道的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.93,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來裡面還摻雜著其他氏族成員做的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.19,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才拼湊出這樣的世界  但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麽調查  都會回到出發點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.78,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有氏族成員夢境的交會點  就只有這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.13,0:16:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.13,0:16:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想查個清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能請您批準嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.85,0:17:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這地方需要這麽嚴肅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了  安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.71,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我去查清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經跳脫這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲和美咲也一定辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿比古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.99,0:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會早就發現了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼不早點說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我說那種蠢話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.46,0:18:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「喂美咲  別再作夢了  趕緊醒醒吧」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好  反正我也有點膩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麽  但你們不可以過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,底下鬧成一片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.65,0:18:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然聖域用得不順手  虛張聲勢倒還沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在飛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.62,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小黑  有什麽動靜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.83,0:18:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種像學園島當時一樣  害怕夢境被拆穿的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.13,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者夢世界本身的變化  或者攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.39,0:19:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前是沒什麽動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.43,0:19:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經做出夢境無法修正的異象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能找出一點對異象的反應就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過目前看來似乎沒特別…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了  有變化嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個人對這變化不為所動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是默默旁觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就中大獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一位白銀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二位青
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪魁禍首就是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三位赤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及最後的綠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打造這個夢境所邀請的成員全都到齊了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個用夢境把我們耍得團團轉的家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  須久那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的一切都不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是虛幻的理想打造成的夢境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麽回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥  就是這小子把我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.77,0:20:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明賦予了你們所追求的理想世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽要自己解除它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話少說  放馬過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.53,0:20:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個惡趣味的權外者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.12,0:20:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽  為什麽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這種場合不是應該要開打的嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.67,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你未經同意就把人關起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家當然會有怨言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.47,0:21:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  你到底是「什麽」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…  - 你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德勒斯登石板吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.19,0:21:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正確來說  是透過碎片殘遺的力量和你們交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.78,0:21:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是力量的本體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小子到底在說些什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德勒斯登石板竟然擁有意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.21,0:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用夢境困住我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們似乎誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.05,0:21:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是從石板被破壞的現場中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個氏族裡挑選一人並實現其願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.51,0:21:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個沒有生離死別的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況  我從來都沒有困住你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.19,0:22:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.86,0:22:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢…消失了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.95,0:22:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.66,0:22:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲  美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.38,0:22:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.71,0:22:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是現任的王 竟然能跟到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.76,0:22:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.10,0:22:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑且先稱呼為「你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.43,0:22:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麽要這麽做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.14,0:22:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就跟石板過去做的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.73,0:22:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是呼應強烈的願望  像這樣實現理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這畢竟是殘餘的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.99,0:22:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能拼湊美好的事物  卻無法太過牢固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.12,0:22:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是給這段日子  透過石板與我連系的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.21,0:23:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些微不足道的回報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.92,0:23:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切不是夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.01,0:23:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們總是想以一句話來概括一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事實不然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.39,0:23:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.35,0:23:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石板中蘊藏的祈願與人心相系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.98,0:23:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成一面巨大的網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已逝去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將誕生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.57,0:23:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這個世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.12,0:23:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡在所有人之間四通八達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.50,0:23:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而就是這樣的網  編織出你們剛才所在的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.92,0:23:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將希望存在的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.75,0:23:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想追求的光景  拼接而成的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.22,0:23:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說  那個流跟磐叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.81,0:24:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是虛假幻象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.73,0:24:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是如假包換的  你們所認識的本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.53,0:24:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才會指派最後的任務給我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.66,0:24:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「讓五條須久那清醒」的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.63,0:24:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.17,0:24:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們明明能可以永遠住下去  為什麽要選擇解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.14,0:24:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這心態是不對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.02,0:24:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是尊哥還是十束哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.39,0:24:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是其他人心中的那些故人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.52,0:24:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去的痛  都是他們不可或缺的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.65,0:24:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不可以自私地抹滅它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.20,0:25:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽見了嗎  王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.83,0:25:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.81,0:25:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你說你無意困住我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.64,0:25:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想離開都是自己的自由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.48,0:25:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真的想走嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.32,0:25:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去原本那個失去所愛  無可挽回的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.74,0:25:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去確實令人不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.07,0:25:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你怎麽能要我們背離現實  在這裡虛擲光陰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.29,0:25:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  吾等大義毫無陰霾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.71,0:25:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  具體的方法是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.84,0:25:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.01,0:26:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要憑自己的意志  刪除理想的光景與裡面的人就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.02,0:26:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.94,0:26:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我過得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.90,0:26:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿迪  還有小黑跟貓  謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.63,0:26:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.09,0:26:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要從這裏繼續前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.55,0:26:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.47,0:26:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也該展翅高飛  前往自己的下一關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.39,0:26:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須久那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.23,0:26:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲別玩過頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.56,0:26:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子別著涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.48,0:26:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學著吃青椒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.40,0:26:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.42,0:27:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田  再給我們喝一杯的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.59,0:27:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽我們就慢慢喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.09,0:27:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.31,0:27:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真難得看到王幫人斟酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.93,0:27:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩位真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.61,0:27:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是最後一次看到這把劍了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.53,0:27:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽  該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.07,0:27:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.58,0:27:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.96,0:27:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白  小黑  吾輩妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對啊  菊理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.71,0:27:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.30,0:28:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來你就放手去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.02,0:28:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿道夫·K·威斯曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:13.69,0:28:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會盡力而為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.11,0:28:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重了  老友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.08,0:28:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你會消失到哪裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.29,0:28:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過  祈願將所有人的心都相系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.84,0:28:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪裡都不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.42,0:28:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且無所不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.88,0:28:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.22,0:28:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就算石板沒了  你也會留下來是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.47,0:28:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.64,0:28:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石板只不過是個接點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.56,0:28:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻是你們人類祈願的化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.86,0:29:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麽強大的力量  原來是祈願嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.61,0:29:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.65,0:29:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.74,0:29:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.78,0:29:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.82,0:29:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.90,0:29:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.95,0:29:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然單一的力量薄弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.95,0:29:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻永無休止的  真摯的祈願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.25,0:29:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到現在也是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.00,0:29:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是  過去是  將來也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.00,0:29:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈願將相系相連  不斷延伸  成為人心的歸宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.97,0:29:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是何等美妙的事呢
